{
  "video_id": "kvdR2TrrZd4",
  "title": "What does a politician's hair say about them? | The Economist",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 6317.0,
      "end_time": 9445.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been drawing for The Economist for 40 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 9445.0,
      "end_time": 11242.0,
      "text": "And during that time I&#39;ve probably drawn"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 11242.0,
      "end_time": 13614.0,
      "text": "every major head of state"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 13614.0,
      "end_time": 17310.0,
      "text": "and covered every major story in the news"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 18483.0,
      "end_time": 20486.0,
      "text": "around the globe."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 20486.0,
      "end_time": 22927.0,
      "text": "What I aspire to do in a caricature"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 22927.0,
      "end_time": 25331.0,
      "text": "is to try to capture a bit of their spirit"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 25331.0,
      "end_time": 28803.0,
      "text": "their personality in the cartoon as I&#39;m drawing them."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 28803.0,
      "end_time": 29636.0,
      "text": "The shape of the head"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 29636.0,
      "end_time": 32366.0,
      "text": "is perhaps the most defining characteristic"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 32366.0,
      "end_time": 33771.0,
      "text": "of any individual."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 33771.0,
      "end_time": 35608.0,
      "text": "However, a key thing to remember"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 35608.0,
      "end_time": 38670.0,
      "text": "the piece that defines the shape of your head"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 38670.0,
      "end_time": 39449.0,
      "text": "more than anything else"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 39449.0,
      "end_time": 41625.0,
      "text": "is the shape of your hair."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 41625.0,
      "end_time": 44636.0,
      "text": "And we all remember Margret Thatcher as The Iron Lady."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 44636.0,
      "end_time": 48384.0,
      "text": "The woman who stood firm and had very fixed views."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 48384.0,
      "end_time": 51342.0,
      "text": "Well her hair was a little like that as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 51342.0,
      "end_time": 52549.0,
      "text": "It was like a brick."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 52549.0,
      "end_time": 55393.0,
      "text": "She needed something that felt iron-clad"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 55393.0,
      "end_time": 58143.0,
      "text": "and her hair was certainly that."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 67332.0,
      "end_time": 68895.0,
      "text": "When it comes to drawing world leaders"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 68895.0,
      "end_time": 70972.0,
      "text": "American presidents are often ones"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 70972.0,
      "end_time": 73167.0,
      "text": "that we tend to draw caricatures of."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 73168.0,
      "end_time": 74629.0,
      "text": "And when it deals with hair"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 74629.0,
      "end_time": 78810.0,
      "text": "there are two presidents in particular who stand out."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 78810.0,
      "end_time": 79995.0,
      "text": "First, Ronald Regan."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 79995.0,
      "end_time": 83412.0,
      "text": "Now Ronald Regan had a really strong coif"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 85235.0,
      "end_time": 88818.0,
      "text": "full head of black lovely cartoonable hair."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 93190.0,
      "end_time": 95131.0,
      "text": "Movie star hair, I mean let&#39;s face it"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 95131.0,
      "end_time": 97559.0,
      "text": "the guy spent a lot of time in front of the camera."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 97559.0,
      "end_time": 101839.0,
      "text": "And his hair was perfectly formed to make him look dynamic"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 101839.0,
      "end_time": 104256.0,
      "text": "young, rugged, like a cowboy."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 105546.0,
      "end_time": 107773.0,
      "text": "The hair also was also kind of a throwback"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 107773.0,
      "end_time": 110920.0,
      "text": "from the 1940s and 1950s"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 110920.0,
      "end_time": 112360.0,
      "text": "the world that Donald Trump"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 112370.0,
      "end_time": 115620.0,
      "text": "would like to think America can go back to."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 121139.0,
      "end_time": 124527.0,
      "text": "Since Ronald Regan, the Presidents of the United States hair"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 124527.0,
      "end_time": 125773.0,
      "text": "has been pretty ordinary."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 125773.0,
      "end_time": 128863.0,
      "text": "But, no discussion of hair is complete"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 128863.0,
      "end_time": 132400.0,
      "text": "unless you include Donald Trump."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 132400.0,
      "end_time": 134441.0,
      "text": "He has this magnificent hair"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 134441.0,
      "end_time": 137500.0,
      "text": "that captured the whole world&#39;s imagination"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 137500.0,
      "end_time": 142238.0,
      "text": "because it both insults physics and it defies gravity."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 142238.0,
      "end_time": 146384.0,
      "text": "It is gold plated, in fact it reminds me of everything"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 146384.0,
      "end_time": 148762.0,
      "text": "that you&#39;d expect in the Trump Tower."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 148762.0,
      "end_time": 151653.0,
      "text": "It also makes a lot of sense to me knowing Donald Trump."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 151653.0,
      "end_time": 153682.0,
      "text": "His face is actually quite ordinary"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 153682.0,
      "end_time": 158655.0,
      "text": "and when he has this magnificent flock of hair on his head"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 158655.0,
      "end_time": 162742.0,
      "text": "he turns into that thing that Donald Trump wants to be"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 162742.0,
      "end_time": 165202.0,
      "text": "the center of attention."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 165202.0,
      "end_time": 170202.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s a person who is big, powerful, stands out in a crowd"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 170622.0,
      "end_time": 174239.0,
      "text": "center of attention, everything that Donald wants"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 174239.0,
